  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, there isn't a wealth of specific, publicly available information detailing employee experiences at National Beverage regarding work-life balance. Employee experiences can vary widely depending on individual roles, departments, and personal circumstances.\n\nIn general, work-life balance can differ across various positions and departments within any organization. Management roles may sometimes demand more hours compared to entry-level or administrative positions. Similarly, departments such as production or operations might have different schedules and demands compared to corporate functions like marketing or HR.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date insights, it would be best to look at employee reviews on platforms like Glassdoor or Indeed, where current and former employees may share their experiences. Additionally, reaching out to someone in the company or networking with employees could provide a clearer picture of the work-life balance at National Beverage.",
